   About 100 people from Lee's hometown of Viroqua, Wis., came to
Florida to watch Friday's scheduled launch of the space shuttle
Atlantis, which was scrubbed 31 seconds before liftoff because of
mechanical problems.
   ``Mark was disappointed, but what can you do,'' said the
astronaut's father, Charles Lee. ``We're going to take one day at a
