   Tehran television Sunday previewed a new
series called ``Top Secret'' to be broadcast each week, showing
confessions of Iranian agents who allegedly worked for the Central
Intelligence Agency.
   The television, monitored in Nicosia, said it would show the
confession of a different exposed agent in each show, to be
